title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-7.11 - Recognition emblems of national quality organizations
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-7.11 - Recognition emblems of national quality organizations

State Regulations
A recognition emblem of a national quality organization
constitutes an advertising sign and is included in the computation of the area
and number of signs. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
646-7.11

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
